Workflow and todo list.

1/ Login Activity: User might need to login, most Flickr API requires auth.
2/ Popular Activity: Once view the most popular tags, and user clicks on a tag in the list.
3/ Thumbnail Activity: Present a list of thumbnails with those tags.

Extra goals:
4/ Popular Activity: User can choose most popular daily vs weekly tags.
5/ Popular Activity: User can choose more than one tag.
6/ Thumbnail Activity: info on top of thumbnail.
7/ Fullscreen Activity: User clicks on thumbnail.
